      <div class="gold-divider"></div>
      <p class="text-cream/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-8">
        In a household with brilliant academicians, Sharath and his siblings took up spiritual sadhanas at a very young age along with their regular schooling. He used to spend his free time exploring places around Palakkad, mostly on his bicycle. Temple festivals, Kathakali, voracious reading, and folk lore were catalysts to the young boy's development.
      </p>
      <p class="text-cream/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
