      </p>
      <p class="text-cream/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
        Through these direct experiences and the wisdom gained through the scriptures, he engages selflessly to guide and transform his fellow-beings.
      </p>
      <p class="text-cream/50 mt-6">He currently resides in Sekharipuram, near Kalpathy in Palakkad with his wife and children.</p>

